    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.05 + (0.41 + (v1 + 0.50 / v1 + 0.03)))
    v2 = wp.abs(v2)
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.63)) * 0.11)
    tmp = (0.26 + wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.19)))
    v2 = wp.sin(v1)
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.21) * (v0 + 0.06 * v0 + 0.55)) * ((tmp + 0.85 - v2 + 0.71) - (v2 + 0.47 / tmp + 0.91)))
    tmp = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.51 * v2 + 0.98) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.78)))
    data[tid] = v0
